phrases: In order to protect something, you need power
and to obtain something requires even greater power.
If you have no power, giving it up is the only option.
And to recover what you have lost...
Yo, so you are Irene Urzaiz, huh?
See what you can do with that.
Fine, tell me what it is you want.
How about we get this task out of the way?
There is nothing to worry about.
Just handle everything like you always do.
You can leave the fighting to me.
Well, not like we will not have to come out guns blazing...
Sorry to keep doing this to you.
It is totally no big deal!
All right, it is almost time, huh?
We cannot have you pondering things before a match.
The thing is... there is something I would like to try out.
I have got to win this match.
No matter who our opponent is, I have no intention of giving up on my wish.
That is why I am here right now.
Neither do I care how we win.
If we can win doing it your way, go right ahead.
We work together, and fight hand in hand.
Remember, we are up against that Gravi-Sheath!
I know it is not going to be easy.
But we are probably only going to get one chance.
Then it will be out of our hands.
It is been one exciting match after another throughout Round 4!
And the grand finale in Sirius Dome will feature Seidoukan Academy's Amagiri/Riessfeld team
vs. the Urzaiz Sisters of Le Wolfe Black Academy!
With the sword inside me, I shall break out of this starry prison...
There it is, there it is!
Amagiri's performance, which is now a well-known sight!
Always a flair for the dramatic, eh?
I see you are bursting with motivation, Amagiri.
I think I will go all-out myself!
The Ser=Veresta is known to burn any object with a fiery slash,
but against a comparable Ogre Luxe, it is a different story!
So the odds are stacked against me in a swordfight, huh?
For a team cobbled together in a couple of months, not bad!
I am impressed that you can evade so well on your own.
Oh, but I am not alone.
We are a team of two, as well.
This power is mine and Priscilla's...
Get out of the way, Ayato!
This is a secret weapon that I have devised for Priscilla.
It will not be easily destroyed.
So we are back to square one, huh?
If you are going to try out that thing, do it fast.
Hey, sorry to keep you waiting.
All right, let us move on to Round Two!
Do you really think that is the right way to do this?
I do not need to hear that from you now.
Amagiri Shinmei Style First Sword, Twin Dragons!
Who would have thought you would go for the Gravi-Sheath?
That was close, but we are out of time, Ayato.
Now it is my turn for payback!
Hate to break it to you, but I am not much of a control artist.
Yeah, but still, I cannot miss with these!
You got to be kidding me...
I can see right through that trap!
This is the ultimate fire skill in my arsenal of setting-type powers.
Do not tell me you held off the blast with the Gravi-Sheath's power?
What on earth is going on here?
Most likely... that is not Irene.
Anyway, we have got to do something or Priscilla will be in danger!
Do not confuse power with what is precious to you!
If it is really precious to you, grab it with both hands!
So which is it that you want right now?!
This match is not over yet!
Well, their school badges have not pronounced them unconscious yet!
Did not you say that you hated being tested?
And the winners of this furious battle are...
Ayato Amagiri and Julis-Alexia von Riessfeld!
Well, I guess that is as much as I could expect.
Amagiri suddenly looks like he is in trouble!
Does this mean that he is sustained significant damage?
No, but this Manadite is clearly...
So Ayato Amagiri can only maintain that power for a specified length of time.
Did I jump the gun, getting the Cats ready?
It is that woman's kid brother.
If there is a red flag, it would be those Jie Long brats,
but it depends on how much they will butt in.
Not to mention, I will have to settle the score with that Arlequint girl.
Damn, what a pain in the ass!
Looks like Amagiri's Prana levels have nosedived.
You never know, that thing he does might not be a performance...
What a pleasure this young boy is.
How will it end up with those guys?
It will be a sight to see!
I thought he was someone to watch out for.
But it looks like he is done after this point.
I would not be so sure.
I think there is another twist in store.
So that young swordsman's got a limiter, too.
Looks like he can only release his power for about five minutes, tops.
Well... it would be child's play for AR-D and RM-C to hold him off for five minutes.
I bet we will be in for an even bigger spectacle!
The battle cannot start soon enough!
Please get ready to stand by!
Seems like I drained too much of your blood.
So how did the match end?
That bastard Amagiri pulverized it like a madman.
Oh, but will not you get yelled at by the student council chairman?
Well, since I did not fulfill my mission, I cannot pay down my debt.
Well, maybe I panicked a little... guess it cannot be helped, right?
I always thought the most important thing was for you to do whatever you wanted.
Because you have always treasured me more than anyone else.
But I want to become strong.
If you are going to fight, Sister, then I want to fight with you.
I do not just want to be protected by you, I want to stand by your side.
I swear I am going to become even more powerful than you!
That is something to look forward to!
Well, your cover's been blown in spectacular fashion.
And thanks to the toll of breaking your seal,
you will not even be able to move that well tomorrow.
Oh well, I will figure something out.
How can you be so optimistic?!
It is not like I am feeling optimistic.
I told you I would have your back, Julis.
What kind of thing is that to just blurt out?
At this rate, I am just going to be doing the same thing over and over, so...
I faced up to this seal, once and for all, you know?
Ayato, do not try to fight alone.
If you are going to have my back,
then I am going to have your back, as well.
You do not really look all right.
Normally, I would want you to take a good, long rest, but...
In that case, I am going to take care of you so you will recover faster.
I-I will take care of you, too!
And I will make you rice balls, too!
Just worry about your own match, you two!
I should be the one to nurse Ayato, as I have no matches.
Needless to say, if you wish, Ayato, I will stay the whole night.
C-Calm down, will you, you guys?
You all have this scary look in your eyes, guys.
Cannot you see Ayato cannot get any rest?!
I wonder how is this going to end?
Thanks to you, I am way behind in my plan.
